Granddaughter has been asking for The Iron Giant for over a year. Found this on Amazon, and the other 3 movies are a great bonus. She loves all of them which makes the 4 hour ride in the car to Nana's house much easier.
You don't get the four movies advertised!!!

The movies from my childhood in full length and on one DVD! I always enjoy buying the DVDs with multiple movies on them, as I have limited space in my dorm room. These movies are exactly what I grew up watching, and they are in full length, and stored in one nice little case. I absolutely adore being able to watch them again by myself or with friends. I've had no problems getting them to play on my laptop, computer, or DVD player. I'm very happy with this purchase.

Bought this 4 pack of movies for my daughter's birthday because she wanted Willie wonka and space jam...the movies I received didn't have either one if those movies, but had kangaroo Jack and iron giant?????  Very disappointed!!!!
